Cloud Vision V1 API - Module Google::Cloud::Vision::V1::Likelihood (v1.16.0)

Reference documentation and code samples for the Cloud Vision V1 API module Google::Cloud::Vision::V1::Likelihood.

A bucketized representation of likelihood, which is intended to give clients highly stable results across model upgrades.
